{"generatedAt":"2026-07-08T07:44:22.832Z","projects_en":[{"id":33,"documentId":"uf9kqzvkiglmvsglsszl0vsx","title":"Youki Sun Tracking App","client":"Youki","date":"2026-05-05","description":"Helping early risers and afternoon sun seekers find the most beautiful skies.","intro":"We've partnered with Youki to design and develop a smartphone app that predicts the quality of sunrises and sunsets before they happen. Drawing on cloud cover, humidity, aerosol density, and sun angle, the app forecasts not just whether a sky will be worth watching, but which colours are likely to appear — helping early risers and afternoon sun seekers find the most beautiful skies.\n\nThe design leans into restraint. Sunrises are already beautifully complex; the interface doesn't need to be. Built bilingually in Japanese and English, the app is being tuned to feel calm and considered — a quiet companion for sky-watchers, there at the right moment when the sky is about to do something remarkable.","body":null,"services":null,"sector":null,"region":"Japan","createdAt":"2026-05-05T21:54:43.962Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-10T09:23:59.288Z","publishedAt":"2026-05-10T09:23:59.425Z","locale":"en","dark_hero":true,"thumbnail":{"id":8,"documentId":"czi855ltofvkzchiq50fer3r","name":"sunrise-app-english.webp","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"focalPoint":null,"width":1750,"height":1226,"formats":{"large":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/large_sunrise_app_english_b6e62e3fe6.webp","hash":"large_sunrise_app_english_b6e62e3fe6","mime":"image/webp","name":"large_sunrise-app-english.webp","path":null,"size":77.83,"width":1000,"height":701,"sizeInBytes":77828},"small":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/small_sunrise_app_english_b6e62e3fe6.webp","hash":"small_sunrise_app_english_b6e62e3fe6","mime":"image/webp","name":"small_sunrise-app-english.webp","path":null,"size":22.77,"width":500,"height":350,"sizeInBytes":22768},"medium":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/medium_sunrise_app_english_b6e62e3fe6.webp","hash":"medium_sunrise_app_english_b6e62e3fe6","mime":"image/webp","name":"medium_sunrise-app-english.webp","path":null,"size":45.68,"width":750,"height":525,"sizeInBytes":45676},"thumbnail":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_sunrise_app_english_b6e62e3fe6.webp","hash":"thumbnail_sunrise_app_english_b6e62e3fe6","mime":"image/webp","name":"thumbnail_sunrise-app-english.webp","path":null,"size":6.26,"width":223,"height":156,"sizeInBytes":6260}},"hash":"sunrise_app_english_b6e62e3fe6","ext":".webp","mime":"image/webp","size":263.92,"url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/sunrise_app_english_b6e62e3fe6.webp","previewUrl":null,"provider":"strapi-provider-upload-strapi-cloud","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2026-05-05T21:54:30.849Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-05T21:54:30.849Z","publishedAt":"2026-05-05T21:54:30.850Z"},"hero_image":null,"images":null,"localizations":[{"id":32,"documentId":"uf9kqzvkiglmvsglsszl0vsx","title":"Youki","client":"Youki","date":"2026-05-05","description":"早朝の空と午後の陽を求める人々に、もっとも美しい空をお届けします。","intro":"Youki様とともに、日の出と日の入りの美しさを予測するスマートフォンアプリの設計・開発を進めています。雲量、湿度、エアロゾル濃度、太陽の角度などをもとに、空が見る価値のあるものになるかどうかだけでなく、どのような色が現れるかまでを予測。早朝の空と午後の陽を求める人々に、もっとも美しい空をお届けします。\n\nデザインは引き算の発想で。日の出はそれ自体が十分に美しく複雑なので、インターフェースまで複雑である必要はありません。日本語と英語のバイリンガル対応で、静かで思慮深い佇まいを目指して調整を重ねています。空が何か特別なことを始めようとする、その瞬間にそっと寄り添う——空を見上げる人のための、控えめな相棒です。","body":null,"services":"Digital Product & Experience Design","sector":null,"region":"Japan","createdAt":"2026-05-10T06:36:19.288Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-10T09:23:59.496Z","publishedAt":"2026-05-10T08:45:04.511Z","locale":"ja","dark_hero":true}]},{"id":47,"documentId":"ejrrnsm6l4cq1majqqv4xkxf","title":"myOCP Online Booking","client":"OCP Group","date":"2026-05-05","description":"Industry first 3-step online booking process for employee counselling program provider OCP.","intro":"While picking up the phone is easy for many, for others, it’s an obstacle between them and the help they need. With employee assistance program provider OCP aware of this issue, we suggested that an overhaul of their existing appointment system was necessary to connect as many workers as possible with the support they deserve.\n\nAvailable on mobile and desktop, this service has revolutionised OCP’s appointment system and prioritised accessibility — users only need to follow three simple steps online to get the support they need.","body":null,"services":"Strategy, Concept Development, UI & UX Design","sector":"Health & Wellness","region":"New Zealand, Australia","createdAt":"2026-05-05T18:56:17.062Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-08T03:12:02.219Z","publishedAt":"2026-07-08T03:12:02.288Z","locale":"en","dark_hero":null,"thumbnail":{"id":24,"documentId":"h6tyr5kttmxg3sicyy4rnk5r","name":"myocp-booking-thumb.webp","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"focalPoint":null,"width":1680,"height":632,"formats":{"large":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/large_myocp_booking_thumb_3427860d01.webp","hash":"large_myocp_booking_thumb_3427860d01","mime":"image/webp","name":"large_myocp-booking-thumb.webp","path":null,"size":22.6,"width":1000,"height":376,"sizeInBytes":22598},"small":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/small_myocp_booking_thumb_3427860d01.webp","hash":"small_myocp_booking_thumb_3427860d01","mime":"image/webp","name":"small_myocp-booking-thumb.webp","path":null,"size":8.61,"width":500,"height":188,"sizeInBytes":8614},"medium":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/medium_myocp_booking_thumb_3427860d01.webp","hash":"medium_myocp_booking_thumb_3427860d01","mime":"image/webp","name":"medium_myocp-booking-thumb.webp","path":null,"size":15.33,"width":750,"height":282,"sizeInBytes":15334},"thumbnail":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_myocp_booking_thumb_3427860d01.webp","hash":"thumbnail_myocp_booking_thumb_3427860d01","mime":"image/webp","name":"thumbnail_myocp-booking-thumb.webp","path":null,"size":3.44,"width":245,"height":92,"sizeInBytes":3444}},"hash":"myocp_booking_thumb_3427860d01","ext":".webp","mime":"image/webp","size":53.23,"url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/myocp_booking_thumb_3427860d01.webp","previewUrl":null,"provider":"strapi-provider-upload-strapi-cloud","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2026-07-08T03:11:50.302Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-08T03:11:50.302Z","publishedAt":"2026-07-08T03:11:50.302Z"},"hero_image":null,"images":null,"localizations":[]},{"id":49,"documentId":"xhfemc31w097ah98ioeiajzy","title":"Zenrise Brand Identity","client":"Zenrise","date":"2026-02-01","description":"Naming, brand identity & collateral design for a Kamakura-based tour agency.","intro":"Zenrise is a Japanese tourism company built around discovering the Japan that doesn't announce itself. The identity needed to match that sensibility — understated, bilingual by principle, and respectful of the experience it frames.\n\nThe palette draws from the natural environment: moss, sand, and salt-bleached greys. Optima Nova anchors the wordmark; Gill Sans, Yu Gothic & Toppan Bunkyu Mincho handle body copy across both languages. Voice and imagery follow the same logic — sensory over transactional, caught in motion rather than posed.\n\nAn identity for a business that believes the best places require a little patience to find.","body":null,"services":"Naming, Brand Identity, Collateral Design","sector":"Tourism","region":"Japan","createdAt":"2026-05-05T18:37:55.696Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-08T03:18:24.146Z","publishedAt":"2026-07-08T03:18:24.243Z","locale":"en","dark_hero":null,"thumbnail":{"id":25,"documentId":"j152rqz3wltjewdox0lbuy9e","name":"zenrise-branding-thumb.webp","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"focalPoint":null,"width":2500,"height":1875,"formats":{"large":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/large_zenrise_branding_thumb_c8c0cea296.webp","hash":"large_zenrise_branding_thumb_c8c0cea296","mime":"image/webp","name":"large_zenrise-branding-thumb.webp","path":null,"size":16.06,"width":1000,"height":750,"sizeInBytes":16058},"small":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/small_zenrise_branding_thumb_c8c0cea296.webp","hash":"small_zenrise_branding_thumb_c8c0cea296","mime":"image/webp","name":"small_zenrise-branding-thumb.webp","path":null,"size":4.3,"width":500,"height":375,"sizeInBytes":4298},"medium":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/medium_zenrise_branding_thumb_c8c0cea296.webp","hash":"medium_zenrise_branding_thumb_c8c0cea296","mime":"image/webp","name":"medium_zenrise-branding-thumb.webp","path":null,"size":8.49,"width":750,"height":562,"sizeInBytes":8488},"thumbnail":{"ext":".webp","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_zenrise_branding_thumb_c8c0cea296.webp","hash":"thumbnail_zenrise_branding_thumb_c8c0cea296","mime":"image/webp","name":"thumbnail_zenrise-branding-thumb.webp","path":null,"size":1.16,"width":208,"height":156,"sizeInBytes":1162}},"hash":"zenrise_branding_thumb_c8c0cea296","ext":".webp","mime":"image/webp","size":188.68,"url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/zenrise_branding_thumb_c8c0cea296.webp","previewUrl":null,"provider":"strapi-provider-upload-strapi-cloud","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2026-07-08T03:17:16.032Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-08T03:17:16.032Z","publishedAt":"2026-07-08T03:17:16.032Z"},"hero_image":null,"images":null,"localizations":[{"id":41,"documentId":"xhfemc31w097ah98ioeiajzy","title":"Zenriseブランドコンセプト","client":"Zenrise","date":"2026-02-01","description":"鎌倉を拠点とするウォーキングツアーのスタートアップのための、ネーミング、ブランドアイデンティティ、及び制作物デザイン。","intro":"Zenriseは、自ら語りかけてこない日本を発見することを軸に据えた、ウォーキングツアーの会社です。そのアイデンティティも同じ感性に従っています――控えめで、バイリンガルであることを原則とし、それが形作る体験を大切にしています。\n\nパレットは自然環境から着想を得ています――苔、砂、そして潮風に褪せたグレー。ワードマークにはOptima Novaを据え、本文にはGill Sans、游ゴシック、凸版文久明朝を用い、両言語にわたって対応しています。ボイスとビジュアルも同じ論理に従っています――取引的なものより感覚的なものを、ポーズなしで、動きの中で捉える。\n\n最良の場所には、少し辛抱強く向き合う価値があると信じる会社のための、アイデンティティ。","body":null,"services":"Naming, Brand Identity, Collateral","sector":"Tourism","region":"Japan","createdAt":"2026-05-05T19:33:19.807Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-10T10:10:58.148Z","publishedAt":"2026-05-10T10:11:00.185Z","locale":"ja","dark_hero":null}]},{"id":46,"documentId":"nqh1spbf9k7gfb0jg2f561yd","title":"OCP Brand Identity","client":"OCP Group","date":"2026-01-01","description":"Rebranding, collateral design & tone of voice for an international health & wellness organisation.","intro":"OCP is Oceania's most responsive employee support network, and their brand needed to catch up with who they'd become. The brief was a refresh that felt professional enough to inspire trust, while remaining warm and approachable for anyone reaching out during a difficult moment — a balance that's harder to achieve than it sounds.\n\nThe new identity is built around a palette of pale and deep blues, with shades of azure and obsidian providing range across applications. Lighter tones set a calm, welcoming mood; darker shades communicate reliability and strength. The typographic system pairs Transat Text with Europa — clean and modern, with enough authority for a professional context.\n\nThe result is a brand that reflects the trust, safety and reassurance OCP brings to workplaces and individuals every day.","body":null,"services":"Brand Identity, Collateral","sector":"Health & Wellness","region":"New Zealand, Australia","createdAt":"2026-05-05T18:51:29.524Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-08T03:10:48.199Z","publishedAt":"2026-07-08T03:10:48.294Z","locale":"en","dark_hero":null,"thumbnail":{"id":23,"documentId":"hvms8lt0bstv0u9zuwdkh66s","name":"ocp-brand-identity-thumb.webp","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"focal