l calm and considered — a quiet companion for sky-watchers, there at the right moment when the sky is about to do something remarkable.","body":null,"services":null,"sector":null,"region":"Japan","createdAt":"2026-05-05T21:54:43.962Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-10T09:23:59.288Z","publishedAt":"2026-05-10T09:23:59.425Z","locale":"en","dark_hero":true}]},{"id":41,"documentId":"xhfemc31w097ah98ioeiajzy","title":"Zenriseブランドコンセプト","client":"Zenrise","date":"2026-02-01","description":"鎌倉を拠点とするウォーキングツアーのスタートアップのための、ネーミング、ブランドアイデンティティ、及び制作物デザイン。","intro":"Zenriseは、自ら語りかけてこない日本を発見することを軸に据えた、ウォーキングツアーの会社です。そのアイデンティティも同じ感性に従っています――控えめで、バイリンガルであることを原則とし、それが形作る体験を大切にしています。\n\nパレットは自然環境から着想を得ています――苔、砂、そして潮風に褪せたグレー。ワードマークにはOptima Novaを据え、本文にはGill Sans、游ゴシック、凸版文久明朝を用い、両言語にわたって対応しています。ボイスとビジュアルも同じ論理に従っています――取引的なものより感覚的なものを、ポーズなしで、動きの中で捉える。\n\n最良の場所には、少し辛抱強く向き合う価値があると信じる会社のための、アイデンティティ。","body":null,"services":"Naming, Brand Identity, Collateral","sector":"Tourism","region":"Japan","createdAt":"2026-05-05T19:33:19.807Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-10T10:10:58.148Z","publishedAt":"2026-05-10T10:11:00.185Z","locale":"ja","dark_hero":null,"thumbnail":{"id":7,"documentId":"imei1xeikrrtzb4mop952yzo","name":"zenrise-revised-concept-a-tagline-mockup.jpg","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"focalPoint":null,"width":2500,"height":1875,"formats":{"large":{"ext":".jpg","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/large_zenrise_revised_concept_a_tagline_mockup_a54027b561.jpg","hash":"large_zenrise_revised_concept_a_tagline_mockup_a54027b561","mime":"image/jpeg","name":"large_zenrise-revised-concept-a-tagline-mockup.jpg","path":null,"size":51.21,"width":1000,"height":750,"sizeInBytes":51214},"small":{"ext":".jpg","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/small_zenrise_revised_concept_a_tagline_mockup_a54027b561.jpg","hash":"small_zenrise_revised_concept_a_tagline_mockup_a54027b561","mime":"image/jpeg","name":"small_zenrise-revised-concept-a-tagline-mockup.jpg","path":null,"size":10.95,"width":500,"height":374,"sizeInBytes":10954},"medium":{"ext":".jpg","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/medium_zenrise_revised_concept_a_tagline_mockup_a54027b561.jpg","hash":"medium_zenrise_revised_concept_a_tagline_mockup_a54027b561","mime":"image/jpeg","name":"medium_zenrise-revised-concept-a-tagline-mockup.jpg","path":null,"size":25.29,"width":750,"height":562,"sizeInBytes":25288},"thumbnail":{"ext":".jpg","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_zenrise_revised_concept_a_tagline_mockup_a54027b561.jpg","hash":"thumbnail_zenrise_revised_concept_a_tagline_mockup_a54027b561","mime":"image/jpeg","name":"thumbnail_zenrise-revised-concept-a-tagline-mockup.jpg","path":null,"size":2.66,"width":208,"height":156,"sizeInBytes":2663}},"hash":"zenrise_revised_concept_a_tagline_mockup_a54027b561","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","size":462.36,"url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/zenrise_revised_concept_a_tagline_mockup_a54027b561.jpg","previewUrl":null,"provider":"strapi-provider-upload-strapi-cloud","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2026-05-05T19:03:58.076Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-05T19:03:58.076Z","publishedAt":"2026-05-05T19:03:58.076Z"},"hero_image":null,"images":null,"localizations":[{"id":49,"documentId":"xhfemc31w097ah98ioeiajzy","title":"Zenrise Brand Identity","client":"Zenrise","date":"2026-02-01","description":"Naming, brand identity & collateral design for a Kamakura-based tour agency.","intro":"Zenrise is a Japanese tourism company built around discovering the Japan that doesn't announce itself. The identity needed to match that sensibility — understated, bilingual by principle, and respectful of the experience it frames.\n\nThe palette draws from the natural environment: moss, sand, and salt-bleached greys. Optima Nova anchors the wordmark; Gill Sans, Yu Gothic & Toppan Bunkyu Mincho handle body copy across both languages. Voice and imagery follow the same logic — sensory over transactional, caught in motion rather than posed.\n\nAn identity for a business that believes the best places require a little patience to find.","body":null,"services":"Naming, Brand Identity, Collateral Design","sector":"Tourism","region":"Japan","createdAt":"2026-05-05T18:37:55.696Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-08T03:18:24.146Z","publishedAt":"2026-07-08T03:18:24.243Z","locale":"en","dark_hero":null}]}],"members":[{"id":8,"documentId":"nla97uiycp75944mojdwcuxm","first_name":"Liam","last_name":"Finlayson","role":"CEO","createdAt":"2026-05-05T18:00:12.936Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-05T18:07:41.193Z","publishedAt":"2026-05-05T18:07:41.268Z","order":1,"portrait":{"id":2,"documentId":"gb6hqnx691f7eho9ninjfqhx","name":"liam-web-photo-2023.png","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"focalPoint":null,"width":874,"height":1165,"formats":{"large":{"ext":".png","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/large_liam_web_photo_2023_34d4f8c921.png","hash":"large_liam_web_photo_2023_34d4f8c921","mime":"image/png","name":"large_liam-web-photo-2023.png","path":null,"size":1372.7,"width":750,"height":1000,"sizeInBytes":1372699},"small":{"ext":".png","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/small_liam_web_photo_2023_34d4f8c921.png","hash":"small_liam_web_photo_2023_34d4f8c921","mime":"image/png","name":"small_liam-web-photo-2023.png","path":null,"size":333.53,"width":375,"height":500,"sizeInBytes":333528},"medium":{"ext":".png","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/medium_liam_web_photo_2023_34d4f8c921.png","hash":"medium_liam_web_photo_2023_34d4f8c921","mime":"image/png","name":"medium_liam-web-photo-2023.png","path":null,"size":766.11,"width":563,"height":750,"sizeInBytes":766112},"thumbnail":{"ext":".png","url":"https://upbeat-approval-82a9e54c20.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_liam_web_photo_2023_34d4f8c921.png","hash":"thumbnail_liam_web_photo_2023_34d4f8c921","mime":"image/png","name":"thumbnail_liam-web-photo